  ### `brightness`

  **Type:** `number`

  **Default:** `undefined`
  
  Adjusts the images `brightness` with the given brightness multiplier. Commonly used together with [`hue`](#hue) and [`saturation`](#saturation).

  **Code example:**
</Markdown>

